_sText:
There are 2 ct spawn points on both south east and south west of the map. 

Terrorists start in the north west. 

There is 2 ladders for each team to get up on top of the containers adding an extra element to the game. 

This is -strictly speaking- a beta3. has been tested with 30 people with no issues. However I will be working on adding HDR and a 3d skybox at a later date however I am working on other projects atm. 

Enjoy :D

Kev
